code: export function createMaze(grid){var newGrid=grid;var row=0;for(var col=0;col<newGrid[0].length;col+=2){for(row=0;row<newGrid.length;row++){newGrid[row][col].isWall=true;}newGrid[generateRandomNumber(newGrid.length)][col].isWall=false;newGrid[generateRandomNumber(newGrid.length)][col].isWall=false;}return newGrid;}function generateRandomNumber(max){return Math.floor(Math.random()*max);}
